'''Paraphernalia''' refers to [[item]]s and [[article]]s required for specific activities. 

*[[Gardening]] paraphernalia would include [[spade]]s, [[hoe]]s, [[auger]]s, etc.
*[[Drug paraphernalia]] might refer to [[hookah]]s, [[water pipe]]s, [[rolling paper]]s, [[hypodermic]] [[syringes]], [[pill]] [[bottle]]s, [[lighter]]s, etc.
*[[Sex toys]] are commonly and [[euphemism|euphemistically]] referred to as paraphernalia.
*[[Fireplace poker]]s are [[firetending]] paraphernalia.
*Items carried in a [[pocketbook]]s may be referred to as paraphernalia.

